WEBVTT

00:14:28.391 --> 00:14:30.039
they would still be too tight.

00:14:30.063 --> 00:14:33.874
AG: Tyler Kantor manages the Bonobos
shop on Madison Avenue in New York.

00:14:34.426 --> 00:14:37.541
He says this wasn't an isolated
incident with buff guys.

00:14:37.565 --> 00:14:39.366
TK: It would happen weekly --

00:14:39.390 --> 00:14:44.057
guy after guy come in,
really feeling kind of dejected

00:14:44.081 --> 00:14:48.745
and these guys have grown up
and lived their entire lives buying pants

00:14:48.769 --> 00:14:52.690
that are one, two, three sizes
too big for them

00:14:52.714 --> 00:14:54.737
so that way it can fit their legs,

00:14:54.761 --> 00:14:57.441
and then they'll have the waist
taken in by a tailor.

00:14:57.465 --> 00:15:00.375
AG: Yeah, I know you're really
feeling sorry for these guys.